Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • Command
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CommandAdd, CommandChange, CommandDisplay, CommandFind, CommandRemove, CommandSearch

    public abstract class Command
extends java.lang.Object
    This abstract class is a template for all of the Commands that can be performed on the Storage object.
